00:11:48.099 --> 00:11:49.540
what has accomplished that we,

00:11:49.540 --> 00:11:51.899
if we've trusted Christ as our savior,

00:11:51.899 --> 00:11:53.860
that we are his sons.

00:11:54.500 --> 00:11:55.739
His children.

00:11:55.739 --> 00:11:57.500
And he loves us.

00:11:57.500 --> 00:12:00.979
And in so loving us, he's given us a Bible

00:12:00.979 --> 00:12:03.739
